Author: gainsforagirl
Text: Oof but I think they are much more recovered than I am. So I think they will be helping me but I don’t want the help. That’s bad to say but I like my ways :(

Author: toucanna
Text: Living in an apartment with others who have EDs is difficult. Make sure you guys are helping each other instead of enabling because it can turn toxic real fast. My ex-friend and current roommate and I exacerbated each other’s eating issues immensely.
